headline: Pattern Welcomes Sue Taylor and Ann Mather to its Board of Directors
summary: SALT LAKE CITY, July 02, 2025--Pattern appoints Sue Taylor and Ann Mather to its board, leveraging their tech and finance expertise from Meta, LinkedIn, and Pixar to drive growth.
